Excuse me , I ’ d like to buy a guitar.Could you recommend one ?
Sure.Do you want an acoustic one or an electric one ?
An acoustic one .
Are you looking to get a steel-string or a classical ?
What ’ s the difference ?
Well , a classical guitar has nylon strings and its neck is bigger than a steel-string guitar ’ s.It ’ s best suited for finger picking . A steel-string is best for playing chords .
